records.short_description: IRIS (Integrated Rx Information System)  : Information request to find out msids of users in prerx who matched drug to rx 454887500 and rx 456527470. Same issue that Sunil figured out how to find who matched the drug in prerx as INC37254742. route to
records.close_notes:
This is the query and attached is the user names that did the drug match as per the data.

select xop.rx_number, xmc.communication_id, xmcd.drug_description med_comm_orig_drug, msib.description med_comm_matched_drug, fu.user_name drug_match_by
from xxiris_med_communications xmc, fnd_user fu, xxiris_om_prescription xop, mtl_system_items_b msib, xxiris_med_communication_data xmcd
where 1=1
--and xmc.communication_id = 4860450721
and fu.user_id = xmc.drug_match_by
and msib.inventory_item_id = xmc.inventory_item_id
and xmcd.communication_id = xmc.communication_id
and xop.rx_id = xmc.rx_id
and msib.organization_id = 81
and xop.rx_number IN (454887500, 456527470);
